channel.title: Need experienced coders for pi 317
channel.description:
Hi guys I am looking for 1-2 rsps coders to work with me on a project. . What I am looking for is someone who has made a couple servers in the past, can patch dupes and glitches, add custom areas/ items, ect. This will be a long project and will reward us both greatly in the future. I have great ideas which NO other servers have and it will make us popular because of it.
Please use this form:
What type of server is your favorite?(317 ect): How much experience do you have in coding?: Why should I choose you?: Willing to split payments for VPS, ect?: Age: Rate yourself 1-10 on your coding: What else can you code apart from rsps?: Hours available per day: Would you prefer coding the server by yourself or with another coder?: Got skype? Add anything notable here:
Please don't post your contact details here. I will PM via Sythe, those who I would like to work with.
Regards,
Amin

item.title: Need experienced coders for pi 317
item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

I’d be glad to help out but here is my thing YOU have to prove that you aren’t an idiot programmer first. I LOVE creating new content but I will NOT work with incompetent programmers. I also do not “patch dupes/glitches” I leave for the other developer(s) as I would be purely content based. (I make what I want in reason of course)
